CDU’s Flosbach Criticizes Finland, Greece Aid Deal, Rheinische Post Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-08-22T22:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-22/flosbach-criticizes-finland-greece-aid-deal-rheinische-says.html
Klaus-Peter Flosbach, the financial
policy spokesman in parliament for Angela Merkel’s  Christian
Democrats , criticized Finland’s collateral arrangement with
Greece,  Rheinische Post  reported today, citing Flosbach.  Countries will be successful in helping Greece when they
join forces, with special conditions for some nations being the
“wrong way,” Flosbach said, according to the German newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
